Install Raspberry Pi OS using Raspberry Pi Imager

Raspberry Pi Imager is the quick and easy way to install Raspberry Pi OS and other operating systems to a microSD card,
 ready to use with your Raspberry Pi.
Watch our 45-second video to learn how to install an operating system using Raspberry Pi Imager.

Download and install Raspberry Pi Imager to a computer with an SD card reader.
Put the SD card you'll use with your Raspberry Pi into the reader and run Raspberry Pi Imager.